ventoy: ventoy (Bootable USB Solution)
ventoy:
ventoy: Ventoy is an open source tool to create bootable USB drives
ventoy: for ISO/WIM/IMG/VHD(x)/EFI files.
ventoy:
ventoy: With Ventoy, you do not need to format the disk repeatedly.
ventoy: Just copy the image files to the USB drive and boot them.
ventoy: You can copy many files at a time and Ventoy will provide
ventoy: a boot menu. It also supports browsing local disk files.
